      "groupIds": [],
      "text": "Conflict Detection (2 heuristics)\n① Cross-collection: top-3 results from\n   ≥2 authoritative collections (OSHA +\n   manuals) with scores within Δ0.15\n② Within-collection: 2+ source files in\n   same collection, best scores within Δ0.15\n   (guard: top score must be ≥ 0.50)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Conflict Detection (2 heuristics)\n① Cross-collection: top-3 results from\n   ≥2 authoritative collections (OSHA +\n   manuals) with scores within Δ0.15\n② Within-collection: 2+ source files in\n   same collection, best scores within Δ0.15\n   (guard: top score must be ≥ 0.50)"
